history.content:
Hey EECS/CS scholars!

Are you a thinker, innovator, a Shark Tank enthusiast, or all of the above? Well, get ready for our very own ‘Bear’ Tank, a mock-Shark Tank event held by the RCSA Corporate Relations committee, where you can present product or policy ideas in front of a panel of professionals working at the forefront of their fields, to win prizes and make connections! Please fill out the form below if you'd be interested in participating, and contact corporate.rcsa@gmail.com if you have any questions. Open to all UC Berkeley students!

Registration/interest form: https://forms.gle/uV5vAWHfagpqjW8b8
history.subject: Opportunity: 'Bear' Tank (mock-Shark Tank) hosted by RCSA
